<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ج ٤٧ - ص <span class="c2">(٢٤٤ - ٢٤٥)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>س ٤٨ - ماذا تعرف عن القرطبي؟ وعن تفسيره؟<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>ج ٤٨ - ص <span class="c2">(٢٤٩ - ٢٥٠)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
